Package org.semanticweb.vlog4j.owlapi

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractClassToRuleConverter
    Abstract base class for converters that create rules from OWL class expressions.
    ClassToRuleBodyConverter
    Helper class for transforming OWL class expressions that occur as subclasses into suitable body literals for rules.
    ClassToRuleHeadConverter
    Helper class for transforming OWL class expressions that occur as superclasses into suitable head literals for rules.
    OwlAxiomToRulesConverter
    Class for converting OWL axioms to rules.
    OwlToRulesConversionHelper
    Utility class for helper functions that are used to convert OWL API objects to rules.
    OwlToRulesConverter
    Class for converting OWL ontologies to rules.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    OwlFeatureNotSupportedException
    Exception that indicates that the translation of OWL into rules has failed due to an expressive feature of OWL that cannot be captured in rules.
